instructions: Put the dinner plate on the table cloth.
Pick up the fork and put it to the left of the dinner plate on the table cloth.
Pick up the salad fork and put it to the left of the dinner fork.
Pick up the dinner knife and place it to the right of the dinner plate.
Pick up the salad knife and place it to the right of the dinner knife.
Pick up the soup spoon and place it to the right of the salad knife.
Pick up the water glass and place it in front of the dinner plate and the knives on the right side.
Pick up the wine glass and place it to the right side of the water glass.
Pick up an additional wine glass and place it next to the other one.
Pick up a coffee cup and place it on the table to the right of the soup spoon.
Pick up the bread plate and place it above the forks.
Pick up a butter knife and place it on the corner of the bread plate.
Pick up a dessert fork, place it above the dinner plate and to the right of the bread plate.
pick up a dessert spoon and place it right above the dessert fork.
Pick up the napkin and place it in the center of the dinner plate.
